channel.title: [Project Insanity] 2006-Reality
channel.description:
Dear moparians,
I have started a new project: 2006-Reality.
The server is not going to be a remake but a unique oldschool looking server, for example; the home is Camelot. I'm trying to achieve a server with the oldschool feeling but not based off something you've seen before.
The recruiting part: [code]What is your name: Where do you come from: How many hours a day do you have available: How long have you been coding project insanity: (Optional)Do you have any projects released, if yes please post: [/code]
Spots filled: [code]Server coders: 3/4[/code]
I'm not looking for a client coder at the moment, but will look for one in the future.
Some media of what the server looks like: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/GcY6t.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/jubbt.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/FOPIz.gif[/img]
